    - m_Type: 0
      Title:
        m_Untranslated: Following the Player - The Basic Way
      Text:
        m_Untranslated: "In this practical, we will continue using the pixel art
          top-down game from previous practicals. So far, the player has been able
          to move, however the camera has not followed the player\u2019s progress,
          and so we haven\u2019t been able to easily explore the game world. \r\nTo
          implement extremely basic following, we can simply attach the camera as
          a child of our player. Recall that child objects will follow the position,
          rotation, and scale of their parent\u2019s transform first before applying
          their own.\r"
